reviewText: This dvd is the truth!!!!!!!!!!!!- I've just started getting into Dr. Juanita Bynum the past few months ,i've heard about her some yrs ago, the lady knows the word. i love her- i wish i had listen to some her dvds,music, etc back then ,but  then again better late than never, i'm so very glad now i have a ear to hear, and also to be introduced to her ministry so to speak.
Dr. Bynum really goes deep into how faith should be applied to one's life.  I truly enjoyed this dvd.  It's a good dvd for a family to watch and study.
